gmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:28:13.000Z","msg":"&quot;你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7R0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=f4c2fc9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>    。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"d7c5666c1c7869f7807976fe6c064093d90fafbd","tid":2153844,"uid":257773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3322c852956326d5e34310ac17448bbbbffe69ad","tid":2153844,"uid":181784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cff9d00d74a8fdaa8d81cf2768bfbf3a95699fc1","tid":2153844,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T20:01:20.000Z","msg":"飲杯啦一齊🍻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T20:36:44.000Z","msg":"飲酒真係好訓 都會想晚晚飲 一教訓天光 咩都唔洗諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"但係第二日會頭痛<br />\n唔知頭痛同心痛邊個難頂啲"},{"pid":"fc05974deaba73eb88044885e1208bac1cb5bb00","tid":2153844,"uid":318720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ec06e8a3974f4c6a4ad06aaa73bb66ddf1b5269","tid":2153844,"uid":181784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87a2c059d6052222744866fea2d61cde4b4e8cf2","tid":2153844,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93d36a4db9a3688f53695bdb5677bdd15416f05b","tid":2153844,"uid":243872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T20:00:03.000Z","msg":"一切只能不斷回望 個內疚感好重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T20:14:39.000Z","msg":"嗯  放過佢就係你最好嘅贖罪"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T20:26:34.000Z","msg":"呢樣我都有諗 想佢搵到真正既幸福"},"citedBy":